{"id":981,"date":"2018-03-23T23:53:55","date_gmt":"2018-03-23T16:53:55","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/toeic.khowebseotop.vn\/?page_id=981"},"modified":"2018-06-04T15:36:23","modified_gmt":"2018-06-04T08:36:23","slug":"gioi-thieu-ve-chung-toi","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/edu1.webtudong8giay.com\/gioi-thieu-ve-chung-toi\/","title":{"rendered":"V\u1ec1 Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Trung t\u00e2m ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef PTC (t\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 Trung T\u00e2m Ngo\u1ea1i Ng\u1eef Ph\u01b0\u1edbc Ti\u1ebfn) \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh l\u1eadp t\u1eeb n\u0103m 1994 v\u00e0 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng trung t\u00e2m d\u1ea1y ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a TP Nha Trang. V\u1edbi b\u1ec1 d\u00e0y kinh nghi\u1ec7m gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y v\u00e0 qu\u1ea3n l\u00ed, PTC l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng trung t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ea1i Nha Trang c\u1ea3 v\u1ec1 qui m\u00f4 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 t\u00edn nhi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a \u0111\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea3o h\u1ecdc vi\u00ean ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef.<\/p>\n<p>Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ch\u00e2m ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a PTC l\u00e0\u00a0<strong>\u201cPh\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n tri th\u1ee9c c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng\u201d<\/strong>. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mong mu\u1ed1n\u00a0<em><strong>\u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn cho c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y v\u00e0 h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef cao v\u1edbi chi ph\u00ed v\u1eeba ph\u1ea3i<\/strong><\/em>.<br \/>\nPTC hi\u1ec7n c\u00f3 c\u00e1c ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh b\u1ed3i d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ti\u1ebfng Anh \u0111a d\u1ea1ng v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 l\u1edbp, s\u1ed1 h\u1ecdc vi\u00ean, ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh h\u1ecdc. Ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh h\u1ecdc t\u1ea1i PTC \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean nhu c\u1ea7u th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf c\u1ee7a h\u1ecdc vi\u00ean v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chia theo nhi\u1ec1u tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00e1c nhau nh\u1eb1m \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 ti\u1ebfp thu ng\u00f4n ng\u1eef cao nh\u1ea5t cho h\u1ecdc vi\u00ean.<\/p>\n<p>PTC hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1edbi\u00a0<strong>m\u1ed9t tr\u1ee5 s\u1edf duy nh\u1ea5t<\/strong>\u00a0<strong>t\u1ea1i 83 Yersin, TP Nha Trang<\/strong>.<br \/>\n<strong><br \/>\n<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"http:\/\/ptc.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/03\/FB-cover-photo-Sept-2016.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-1357 size-large\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/ve-giuseart-981.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" srcset=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/ve-giuseart-981.jpg 1024w, http:\/\/ptc.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/03\/FB-cover-photo-Sept-2016-300x111.jpg 300w, http:\/\/ptc.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/03\/FB-cover-photo-Sept-2016-768x284.jpg 768w, http:\/\/ptc.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/03\/FB-cover-photo-Sept-2016-640x237.jpg 640w, http:\/\/ptc.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/03\/FB-cover-photo-Sept-2016-940x348.jpg 940w, http:\/\/ptc.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/03\/FB-cover-photo-Sept-2016-150x56.jpg 150w\" width=\"640\" height=\"237\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p><strong>6 l\u00ed do t\u1ea1i sao b\u1ea1n n\u00ean ch\u1ecdn PTC<br \/>\n<\/strong><br \/>\n1.\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0<strong>Uy t\u00edn ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y v\u00e0 h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp<\/strong>.<\/p>\n<p>2.\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0<strong>M\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef sinh \u0111\u1ed9ng tr\u00ean l\u1edbp<\/strong>.<\/p>\n<p>3.\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0<strong>\u0110\u1ed9i ng\u0169 gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean c\u00f3 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef v\u1eefng v\u00e0ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o s\u01b0 ph\u1ea1m ch\u00ednh quy.<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>4.\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0<strong>Ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh h\u1ecdc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf theo chu\u1ea9n qu\u1ed1c gia v\u00e0 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf<\/strong><strong><br \/>\n<\/strong>B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh gi\u00e1o tr\u00ecnh ch\u00ednh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ecdn l\u1ecdc t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng gi\u00e1o tr\u00ecnh m\u1edbi v\u00e0 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n nay, PTC c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y th\u00eam nh\u1eefng gi\u00e1o tr\u00ecnh h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00f3a h\u1ecdc nh\u1eb1m gi\u00fap t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng k\u0129 n\u0103ng h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp c\u1ee7a h\u1ecdc vi\u00ean. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh h\u1ecdc \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 chu\u1ea9n \u0111\u1ea7u ra t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1ee9ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 qu\u1ed1c gia (ch\u1ee9ng ch\u1ec9 A-B-C, B\u1ed9 GD-\u0110T) v\u00e0 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf (Cambridge ESOL, TOEIC, TOEFL, IELTS).<\/p>\n<p>5.\u00a0\u00a0<strong>Trang thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i<\/strong>.<br \/>\nT\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c ph\u00f2ng h\u1ecdc \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trang b\u1ecb thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb \u0111a ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ti\u1ec7n (multimedia) nh\u01b0 m\u00e1y t\u00ednh, TV LCD, m\u00e1y chi\u1ebfu v\u00e0 m\u00e1y \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00f2a.<\/p>\n<p>6.\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0<strong>T\u01b0 v\u1ea5n th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf.<\/strong><strong><br \/>\n<\/strong>Cung c\u1ea5p nh\u1eefng \u00fd ki\u1ebfn t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf gi\u00fap h\u1ecdc vi\u00ean v\u00e0o \u0111\u00fang l\u1edbp, h\u1ecdc \u0111\u00fang ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp ho\u1eb7c ngh\u1ec1 nghi\u1ec7p l\u00e2u d\u00e0i c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n, ho\u1eb7c gi\u00fap c\u00e1c doanh nghi\u1ec7p\/ c\u01a1 quan x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng c\u00e1c ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 &amp; b\u1ed3i d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef cho nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean\/ c\u00e1n b\u1ed9 c\u00f4ng nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Trung t\u00e2m ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef PTC (t\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 Trung T\u00e2m Ngo\u1ea1i Ng\u1eef Ph\u01b0\u1edbc Ti\u1ebfn) \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh l\u1eadp t\u1eeb n\u0103m 1994 v\u00e0 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng trung t\u00e2m d\u1ea1y ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a TP Nha Trang. V\u1edbi b\u1ec1 d\u00e0y kinh nghi\u1ec7m gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y v\u00e0 qu\u1ea3n l\u00ed, PTC l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng trung t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng [&#8230;]\n","protected":false},"author":5,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"page-right-sidebar.php","meta":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/edu1.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/981"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/edu1.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/edu1.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/edu1.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/5"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/edu1.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=981"}],"version-history":[{"count":2,"href":"https:\/\/edu1.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/981\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":1249,"href":"https:\/\/edu1.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/981\/revisions\/1249"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/edu1.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=981"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}